msgid "on the WooCommerce / FluentCart checkout a required acknowledgement tick-box is added automatically. The button stays visible until the consumer ticks it; only then is it hidden for this item. On other checkouts/platforms the button stays (fail-safe). For the digital reason you must also deliver a durable-medium (e-mail) confirmation to the consumer before access begins."
